{"tid":1754573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"根據警察入職要求，藍衫起薪係1萬4、白衫起薪係2萬2","createTime":"2019-11-25T09:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T09:21:28.000Z","uid":128761,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fd6cdfa12806caa4c7da887ab8465656f0344206","tid":1754573,"uid":128761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:07:45.000Z","msg":"政府公務員唔同職系既人工係點定？<br />\n其實最主要係睇個份工既入職要求，其次係工作難度／職系既企硬程度<br />\n<br />\n以藍衫警為例，佢地入職要求係DSE五科二，係屬於「香港中學文憑考試職系」第一組<br />\n依組既職系起薪為PT3 ($14,780)，係咪好眼熟呢，依個正正係ACO既起薪<br />\n公道D講，警察要返shift、要執法，工作既難度同挑戰真係高過ACO<br />\n咁咪加多2個pt，即係$16,790頂到盡<br />\n（警察薪級表同普通公務員唔同，但廢事太複雜所以用普通公務員薪級表簡化D先)<br />\n<br />\n而白衫警又點？白衫警人職要求係需要香港中學文憑考試五科第三級或同等成績(或香港高級程度會考兩科及格和香港中學會考三科良)職系，即係「香港中學文憑考試職系」第三組<br />\n依組既職系起薪為PT10 ($22,865)，點解又咁眼熟？<br />\n因為依個起薪正正係以前所謂2A3O既職系既起薪<br />\n都係個句，警察要返shift、要執法（但其實2A3O既工作難度唔會低過白衫警）<br />\n當好好人加多2個pt，即係$25,790<br />\n當你有埋大學學歷，咁再加多2個pt，頂到最最最盡係$28,725 (pt14)<br />\npt14係唔少學位職系既起薪，所以都係好合理既人工<br />\n<br />\n總括而言，警察（包括其他所有紀律部隊，老實講全部都係overpaid）人工既合理水平：<br />\n藍衫警：$16,790<br />\n白衫警：$25,790 - $28,725 (視為學歷而定）<br />\n<br />\n而家既起薪係要求既1.5倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日話高薪養廉，但香港有icac(雖然得個名)<br />\n同埋衰d講，要貪污，人工多一萬都係會貪，比起貪污既金額，人工根本唔會cover得哂"},{"pid":"6c08adcb5c3a86c369e392434b2e7a59b6f51d43","tid":1754573,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:07:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">依家我哋區選贏咗，外國好關注我哋！<br />\n係咪連少少嘢都唔肯做呀？</span><br />\n<br />\n最新的tweets 一定響bot <br />\n總之<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> Retweet Like Reply </span></span>就得<br />\n㩒入👉 <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJjk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=d3399290\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">/task</span></span> 攞任務<br />\n<br />\nSen. Marco Rubio<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1198773889112956928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1198773889112956928&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJjk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=775f69d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1198773889112956928&h=2dc87735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1198773889112956928</a><br />\n<br />\nSen. Rick Scott<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1198739997911846913\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1198739997911846913&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJjk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=3304ac05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1198739997911846913&h=291b9b3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1198739997911846913</a><br />\n<br />\nSen. Marsha Blackburn<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/MarshaBlackburn/status/1198773803976810496\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMarshaBlackburn%2Fstatus%2F1198773803976810496&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJjk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=517c7d2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMarshaBlackburn%2Fstatus%2F1198773803976810496&h=03c18e02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/MarshaBlackburn/status/1198773803976810496</a><br />\n<br />\n更加多嘅tweet請入bot搵<br />\n<br />\n（twitter戰線)國際都關注今次香港的區選<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754022</a>"},{"pid":"811d1a8b25df6b9064a6cc25449fb2c3c6be8aa8","tid":1754573,"uid":150651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:09:27.000Z","msg":"咁低人工無人會做 我做看更印印腳都唔止啦<br />\n<br />\n提高學歷需求實際d"},{"pid":"8f6d06ad02d767cf7ff6205296735e86b7f73725","tid":1754573,"uid":128761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"811d1a8b25df6b9064a6cc25449fb2c3c6be8aa8","tid":1754573,"uid":150651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:09:27.000Z","msg":"咁低人工無人會做 我做看更印印腳都唔止啦<br />\n<br />\n提高學歷需求實際d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:11:43.000Z","msg":"警察辛苦d，但人工高aco少少，可能會少d大學生爭，但一樣大把人爭<br />\n白衫警有2萬5-2萬8更加已經係算高人工，講緊高一個pt既EO都萬幾人爭百幾個位"},{"pid":"e637295174f0052620e7e9b1166e90e2d946ad8c","tid":1754573,"uid":2764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:12:03.000Z","msg":"岩 推"},{"pid":"0d5b32b027aa8cbd6cbba98b3f87831d4c7027de","tid":1754573,"uid":128761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:14:00.000Z","msg":"太高人工搞到佢地以為自己好勁，d人又會驚<br />\n老實講犯要驚警察係正常<br />\n但正常市民係唔需要驚，亦唔需要覺得自己低佢地一等<br />\n佢地係公務員，係服務市民，係要驚因為做唔好野而比市民鬧<br />\n而唔係用個勢同人工去睇低d市民"},{"pid":"44d83fb41985f9c5b2e03b5bf632dc79295a4f80","tid":1754573,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:15:24.000Z","msg":"減人工啦，同市民共渡時間"},{"pid":"5188dcf1e0769e85f98df40fc5c1d08d6c0311a1","tid":1754573,"uid":289978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:16:45.000Z","msg":"好快俾人減人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e295137e9ea9427378310ab3210ae5ad6b334293","tid":1754573,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:18:05.000Z","msg":"加強icac權力，換哂偏垃圾支政<br />\n<br />\n狗唔敢囂張"},{"pid":"c30a368941ad5877171533706b3e64c1d31363ab","tid":1754573,"uid":128761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f6d06ad02d767cf7ff6205296735e86b7f73725","tid":1754573,"uid":128761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"811d1a8b25df6b9064a6cc25449fb2c3c6be8aa8","tid":1754573,"uid":150651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:09:27.000Z","msg":"咁低人工無人會做 我做看更印印腳都唔止啦<br />\n<br />\n提高學歷需求實際d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:11:43.000Z","msg":"警察辛苦d，但人工高aco少少，可能會少d大學生爭，但一樣大把人爭<br />\n白衫警有2萬5-2萬8更加已經係算高人工，講緊高一個pt既EO都萬幾人爭百幾個位"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:19:59.000Z","msg":"同埋點解減人工反而會好d<br />\n係因為依家d廢柴yijin仔貪人高人工先入去<br />\n減左人工，佢地點會做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而有心有力但可能學歷真係未夠高(hd/asso)就會去做<br />\n<br />\n更加可取既係將ia個套既人手編制放入警察度<br />\nia點解特別多大學生爭係因為升sia好快，基本上5,6年一定得<br />\n但警察升警長係以10年15年計<br />\n可取既做法係取消高級警員職級，比pc仔5、6年就升警長<br />\n當然人工都唔係好似依家警長咁高<br />\n只係當升職機會大、流動力比較高，自然又會吸引到較高學歷既人去做"},{"pid":"bdd7ae8a5f8d46fb1f90a3454166a0fd0486f6bf","tid":1754573,"uid":248578,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:21:28.000Z","msg":"客觀講做警察係比普通文職辛苦同埋需要更多技能(警例,使用武力方法),又要入學堂軍訓<br />\n高過文職係正常<br />\n但而家PC仔26K, 督察47K人工完全係高到離撚譜<br />\n個人意見PC仔 20K, 督察35K係合理水平"}]}